snippet.title: FilmRise Movies
snippet.description:
FilmRise Movies is a free-to-watch treasure trove of hit films starring your favorite actors. Our impressive catalogue includes beloved cult classic DONNIE DARKO with Jake and Maggie Gyllenhaal; John Cusack / Morgan Freeman thriller THE CONTRACT; acclaimed crime drama BAD LIEUTENANT: PORT OF CALL NEW ORLEANS featuring screen legends Nicolas Cage and Eva Mendes; and much more, always completely free.

#action #thrillers #actionmovies #freemovies #fullmovies

FilmRise Movies is operated by FilmRise, one of the most recognized film & television distribution companies and streaming networks in the world — offering over 40,000 movies, classic television shows, festival indies, family favorites, documentaries and foreign language releases. FilmRise content can be found in theaters, on the free FilmRise Apps and on many popular streaming platforms including Amazon Prime Video, Peacock, The Roku Channel, Netflix, HBO Max, Pluto TV, iTunes and more. For more info, visit the links below!
